@startuml
participant AppShell
participant NotificationStreamService
participant NotificationService
participant NotificationBell
participant ToastService

AppShell -> NotificationStreamService : start SSE
NotificationStreamService -> NotificationService : GET /notifications/stream
NotificationService --> NotificationStreamService : notification event
NotificationStreamService --> NotificationBell : update unread count
NotificationStreamService --> ToastService : emit toast if visible
@enduml
